Package com.ftp.file

Class FTPFile

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ftp.file.FTPFile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class FTPFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is replacement for File class in standard Java library. It is used for keeping file properties after serialization because Java's File doesn't keep field values after deserializing.
    See Also:
